Package spoon.support.visitor.replace

Class ReplacementVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • spoon.reflect.visitor.CtScanner
      • spoon.support.visitor.replace.ReplacementVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CtVisitor
    public class ReplacementVisitor
extends CtScanner
    Used to replace an element by another one. This class is generated automatically by the processor spoon.generating.ReplacementVisitorGenerator.
